data.description: Charming 1950s home updated while the original character shines through in the carefully preserved details. This 4-bed, 2-bath gem includes a bonus office space. Features an open and spacious living area complemented by a functional kitchen. Preserved original hardwood floors with a combination of LVP flooring in the bedrooms. New windows throughout and LED lighting. New gas furnace, range and water heater. A brand new deck in your backyard and an extended driveway makes for the perfect space to host for the holidays. Conveniently located near a high school, hospital, and grocery stores. Perfect home for a growing family.
